CustomField.formula: If ( Not(IsNull ( Set_Up_Employer_Contributions__c)) && Not ( IsNull ( Enrollments_and_Waivers_Entered__c )), ( Enrollments_and_Waivers_Entered__c - Set_Up_Employer_Contributions__c - 2*( floor((Enrollments_and_Waivers_Entered__c - DATE(1985, 6, 24))/7) - floor((Set_Up_Employer_Contributions__c- DATE(1985, 6, 24))/7))),Null)
